"    </li>",
"    <li>",
"     Eiff, MP, Hatch, RL, Calmbach, WL. Carpal fractures. In: Fracture management for primary care, 2nd ed. Chpt.5. Saunders, Philadelphia, Pa. 2003.",
"    </li>",
