"     Seitz WH Jr, Papandrea RF. Fractures and dislocations of the wrist. In: Rockwood and Green's Fractures in Adults, 5th, Bucholz RW, Heckman JD (Eds), Lippincott, Williams, &amp; Wilkins, 2002 2002.",
